Privacy Policy

Last updated: 10 January 2026

Overview

Your privacy is important to us. This app is designed to work entirely offline and does not collect, store, or share personal data.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information.

Specifically:

No accounts or sign-ups

No names, emails, or identifiers

No location data

No analytics or tracking

No advertising identifiers

Data Stored on Your Device

The app stores checklist data locally on your device only, such as:

Checked items

Custom items you add

This data:

Never leaves your device

Is not synced to any server

Is not accessible to us

Is deleted automatically if you delete the app

Sharing

When you use the Share feature (text or PDF), the content is shared only when you explicitly choose to share it, using iOS system sharing tools.
We do not receive or store any shared content.

Third-Party Services

This app does not use third-party SDKs, analytics tools, or advertising services.

